====Usage notes====
This character form is not found in the {{w|Kangxi dictionary}} and is not used in Japan or Korea ({{l|mul|啓}} is used instead). It is the preferred form used in Hong Kong and Taiwan; historically the preferred form is {{l|mul|啓}} in Hong Kong, but this has shifted in recent years.

