===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Shu-ta Yang: {{Han compound|ls=ic|戶|又|t1=door|t2=hand}} — to open a door with the hand. Later, {{och-l|*口}} was added and {{och-l|*又}} evolved to {{och-l|*攴}}.

